1. *Centra* grada je prepun turista. (The *center* of the city is full of tourists.)
2. Železnička *stanica* se nalazi u *centru* grada. (The train *station* is located in the *center* of the city.)
3. Druženje sa prijateljima je najbolje u *centru* grada. (Hanging out with friends is best in the *city center*.)
4. Većina firmi ima svoje sedište u *centru* grada. (Most companies have their headquarters in the *city center*.)
5. *Centar* za kulturu organizuje brojne kulturne manifestacije. (The *cultural center* organizes numerous cultural events.)
6. Kupovina u *tržnom centru* može biti zabavna aktivnost. (Shopping in a *shopping center* can be a fun activity.)
7. *Centar* za istraživanje raka sprovodi važna medicinska istraživanja. (The *cancer research center* conducts important medical research.)
8. Studenti često borave u *studentskom centru* tokom pauze između predavanja. (Students often stay in the *student center* during breaks between lectures.)
9. *Centar* za obuku vozača organizuje kurseve za sticanje vozačke dozvole. (The *driving school center* offers courses for obtaining a driver's license.)
10. *Centar* za socijalni rad pruža pomoć ugroženim građanima. (The *social welfare center* provides assistance to vulnerable citizens.)